-- Ergo to Triple Litigation Funding Business, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2011-12-21T07:34:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-21/ergo-to-triple-litigation-funding-business-handelsblatt-reports.html
Munich Re’s Ergo unit plans to
triple litigation funding in the next three years as rival
 Allianz SE (ALV)  scales back its business in that area,  Handelsblatt 
reported today, citing an interview with Thomas Kohlmeier, who
heads Ergo’s Legial division.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
